item.title: CVE-2019-3766|2024-09-17T02:01:43.249Z -- dell -- elastic%20cloud%20storage
item.description: Dell EMC ECS versions prior to 3.4.0.0 contain an improper restriction of excessive authentication attempts vulnerability. An unauthenticated remote attacker may potentially perform a password brute-force attack to gain access to the targeted accounts.
